.TH RON 1 "February 2026" "Ron Bot v1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
ron \- friendly Discord bot with weather, wellness, and motivation features

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ron-start
.br
.B ron-stop
.br
.B ron-status

.SH DESCRIPTION
Ron is a friendly Discord bot providing weather information, wellness reminders, motivational features, and quality-of-life commands designed to help users stay healthy, hydrated, and motivated.

The bot connects to Discord and responds to both prefix commands (default: \fB!\fR) and slash commands (\fB/\fR).

.SH COMMANDS

.SS Weather & Location
.TP
.B /weather \fICITY\fR
Get current weather for any city with temperature, humidity, wind speed, and weather-appropriate emojis. Uses the free wttr.in API.

Example: \fB/weather London\fR or \fB!weather "New York"\fR

.SS Fun & Games
.TP
.B /ping
Check bot latency and response time in milliseconds.

.TP
.B /roll \fINdM\fR
Roll dice using NdM format (N = number of dice, M = sides per die).

Examples: \fB/roll 2d6\fR, \fB!roll d20\fR, \fB!roll 3d8\fR

Supports up to 100 dice maximum.

.TP
.B /quote
Send a random motivational quote from 22+ inspirational sources including Steve Jobs, Eleanor Roosevelt, and Vince Lombardi.

.SS Wellness & Health
.TP
.B /waterreminder
Subscribe or unsubscribe from hourly water hydration reminders. The bot will send hourly DM reminders with encouraging messages to stay hydrated.

.TP
.B /workout
Get a random workout suggestion with full instructions. Includes quick desk stretches (2 minutes), cardio options, strength training, and full yoga flows.

.TP
.B /breathing
Guided breathing exercise to reduce stress and improve focus. Four different exercise types:
- Box Breathing (4-4-4-4)
- 4-7-8 Breathing (relaxation)
- Belly Breathing (grounding)
- Energizing Breath (quick energy boost)

.TP
.B /tip
Get a daily wellness tip covering topics like sleep, nutrition, movement, mindfulness, social connection, and goals.

.TP
.B /motivate
Quick motivational affirmation boost for when you need encouragement.

.SS Reminders
.TP
.B /remind \fIMINUTES MESSAGE\fR
Set a personal DM reminder that will be sent after the specified number of minutes.

Examples:
  \fB/remind 10 Take a break\fR
  \fB!remind 30 Drink water and stretch\fR
  \fB/remind 60 Check your email\fR

.SS Information & Management
.TP
.B /help
Show all available commands with descriptions and usage examples.

.TP
.B /about
Display information about Ron Bot, its features, and available commands.

.TP
.B !sync
Manually synchronize slash commands with Discord. This is an owner-only command and should be run after updating bot commands.

.SH INSTALLATION

.SS Quick Install
.nf
cd /path/to/Ron
./scripts/install_all.sh
.fi

This script will:
.RS
- Create Python virtual environment
- Install dependencies from requirements.txt
- Set up .env configuration
- Create global symlinks (ron-start, ron-stop, ron-status)
.RE

.SS Manual Install
.nf
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your DISCORD_TOKEN
python3 ron_bot.py
.fi

.SH USAGE

.SS Starting the Bot
.nf
ron-start              # Using symlink (if installed)
./scripts/run_ron.sh   # Direct script
.fi

.SS Stopping the Bot
.nf
ron-stop               # Using symlink
./scripts/stop_ron.sh  # Direct script
.fi

.SS Checking Status
.nf
ron-status             # Using symlink
./scripts/ron-status.sh # Direct script
.fi

.SS Systemd Integration
Install as systemd --user service for auto-start on login:
.nf
./scripts/install_systemd_user.sh
systemctl --user enable ron.service
systemctl --user start ron.service
systemctl --user status ron.service
.fi

.SS Viewing Logs
.nf
tail -f ron.log              # Real-time log
tail -50 ron.log             # Last 50 lines
grep ERROR ron.log           # Errors only
.fi

.SH CONFIGURATION

.SS Environment Variables
Required in \fB.env\fR file:

.TP
.B DISCORD_TOKEN
Your Discord bot token from the Developer Portal. Required for bot operation.

.TP
.B PREFIX
Command prefix (default: \fB!\fR). Change to customize prefix for your server.

Example \fB.env\fR:
.nf
DISCORD_TOKEN=your_token_here
PREFIX=!
.fi

